title: RBF - Best of Us... For the Rest of Us [BBBDV][2011]
description: Reel Big Fish is a southern California ska punk band who broke into the mainstream in the mid to late 1990s after the success of No Doubt and Sublime. Reel Big Fish is now more well known, but not quite mainstream in the USA and Europe. Although thought by many to be an actual "ska" band, Reel Big Fish is more of a rock band with ska elements, playing off of the genre from when it was popular in the mid 90s, commonly referred to as third wave
